Package acg.architecture.view.glyph.loader

Contains the glyph loader for reading glyph configuration files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    A_Entry
    Defines shared elements of an entry that is indexed for ordering.
    EntryCircle
    Defines a circle entry as a vertex, radius, and color on an arbitrary coordinate system.
    EntryColor
    Defines a color entry.
    EntryEdge
    Defines an edge entry as a line between two vertices and a color.
    EntryMap<_ENTRY_ extends A_Entry>
    Defines a generic map for any entry.
    EntryVertex
    Defines a vertex as an (x,y,z) point on an arbitrary coordinate system.
    GlyphLoader
    Defines the loader that reads in a layout configuration file with the edges and circles.
    LayoutBundle
    Defines a collection of edge lists and circles.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidLayoutException
    Defines an exception for layout errors in the glyph loader.

Package acg.architecture.view.glyph.loader Description
